headline: Fiserv Expands Advisory Services for Financial Institutions with Acquisition of Smith Consulting Group
summary: MILWAUKEE, September 25, 2025--Fiserv announced the acquisition of Smith Consulting Group, an operational consulting service utilized by community banks and credit unions in the US
